NB: These functions only works when the current block number is > bond. endBlock

- to deposit the first time you call the deposit function

```
bondingV2.connect(signer).deposit(amount, duration)
``` 

- to withdraw LP tokens from a bonding share (that is not locked)

```
bondingV2.connect(signer).removeLiquidity(amount, bondingShareID)
``` 

- to add LP tokens to a bonding share (that is not locked)

```
bondingV2.connect(signer).addLiquidity(amount, bondingShareID, duration)
```

